briefTitle: A Study in Japanese Participants With Moderate-to-Severe Psoriasis
officialTitle: A Multicenter, Open-Label, Long-Term Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of LY2439821 in Japanese Patients With Moderate-to-Severe Psoriasis
summary: This study will assess the safety and efficacy of ixekizumab in participants with moderate to severe psoriasis in Japan.
